import { Route, Router, Routes } from 'react-router-dom'
import './App.css'
import Join from './pages/Join'
import Login from './pages/Login'

function App() {
  return (
    <>
      <Routes>
        <Route path="/join" element={<Join />} />
        <Route path="/login" element={<Login />} />
      </Routes>
    </>
  )
}

export default App
